title: Operation Endgame: Authorities Takedown 1,025 Servers Linked to Rhadamanthys, VenomRAT, and Elysium

content.raw: Between November 10 and 14, 2025, law enforcement agencies executed one of the most significant coordinated operations against cybercriminals in recent history. Operation Endgame, coordinated from Europol’s headquarters in The Hague, successfully dismantled three major threats to global cybersecurity: the infamous Rhadamanthys infostealer, the VenomRAT remote access trojan, and the Elysium botnet.
